Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有邂逅 就定然会有离别之日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是没有办法的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 若没有邂逅 就不会有珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 离别的眼泪有一半是感谢的眼泪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 让人害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 今天为了领取送去做定期检查的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和艾莉西亚前辈来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做思科威尔的凤尾舟工房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 每一艘凤尾舟都是匠人们手工制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作一艘凤尾舟大概要花三个月左右的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用年限约为20年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每隔几年都必须为凤尾舟进行一次全面保养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘凤尾舟虽然已经用了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是我重要的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 定期检查的结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为已经用了蛮长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还很好用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…如果只是自己用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是说句实话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已经残旧到让客人乘坐会显得失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那保留下来作练习用呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样凤尾舟就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用次数减少的话 会加快老旧的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不能让客人乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但用作搬运的话还能用很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在每天都会使用它的主人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直工作到使用年限为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对凤尾舟来说也是件幸福的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:12.43,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 与凤尾舟的分别…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然分别会很寂寞 但也不能对客人失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大叔说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够跟每天使用自己的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘凤尾舟一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 明天你带上相机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟这艘凤尾舟一起去值得纪念的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是明天应该帮艾莉西亚前辈工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是灯里用的凤尾舟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是真的凤尾舟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟先生 今天开始请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水无灯里 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好哦 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…有句话不知该怎么说好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你划的方向反了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要照好多照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相机好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气也很好～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 凤尾舟先生再见之旅启程～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…咦咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…对不起 对不起 对不起 对不起…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不过今天找我到底什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凤尾舟先生再见之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实今天出来是为了跟这艘凤尾舟作最后的纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已经破损得不能再搭载乘客了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定换一艘新的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生是我用这艘凤尾舟接待的第一位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想请你参加这次行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就走第一次接待晓先生时的路线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子 载我去开往浮岛的缆车站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 是客人吗 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 记得今天好像有检查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缆车只开到六点为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六点…还有十五分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赶上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…以我的技术没办法赶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是只付半熟手的船钱哦 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我不是你的客人吗 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只是半熟手 不也是领航员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 请允许我使用遮挡客人视线的划法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 这就是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天陪我走这一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛一脸认真啊 马尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 爱丽丝 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小后辈是这个行动下一程的参加者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走好你的第二次人生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是热血沸腾的男人 气候调节员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将眼泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去跟两位前辈初次见面的那个岬角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次只拍凤尾舟们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是给它添了许多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强它做了许多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 谁叫它是你的凤尾舟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它肯定在想 唉 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像凤尾舟们也在谈话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道别会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在说让人害羞的台词哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也坐过很多次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就没哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个啊…那个…红茶的水汽跑到眼睛里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是凤尾舟先生再见之旅其三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的路线是单手套晋级考试的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试时有不告诉考生这里就是考试地点的传统呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时侯我也是完全不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考试的时候还是第一次来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时还以为被水攻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个让人昏昏入睡的悠闲静谧的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里被领航员们称为「希望之丘」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望之丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里可以把新威尼斯尽收眼底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格 恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里今天开始就是单手套了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 我们来照相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…您什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就一直坐着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能开始划了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但我还是半熟手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要到哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到前面的分岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 您为什么会在我的凤尾舟上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是缘分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缘分吗 真是个美丽的词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能…再坐一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这样 再划一段好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我第一次划凤尾舟时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们去吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 明天就是跟凤尾舟分别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 我已经坐不上那艘凤尾舟了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想好好跟它说再见啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 雨夜后的黎明…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
