Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:55.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:06.40,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:14.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:24.75,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:33.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顔が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:44.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:54.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:59.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:36.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:45.91,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:55.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:06.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:00:00.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:24.75,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:33.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:44.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:54.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:59.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
